[A previous report in the same newspaper has mentioned the total number of cases from Balochistan province at 27 [Crimean-Congo hem. fever - Pakistan (15): Balochistan 20160905.4465412].The reported cases seems to have similar course and age but the report did not clarify the hospital facility, and whether the CCHF diagnosis was lab confirmed. Correct information by province/region would be appreciated from the relevant public health officials. - Mod.UBA

Maps of Pakistan can be seen at http://www.mapsofworld.com/pakistan/pakistan-political-map.html and https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=4468767,140. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]
